Add Thumbnail

 

To add thumbnail for a System Object use Add Thumbnail action.

If the system object has already a thumbnail a Confirm message is displayed

In the dialog:

  1. Enter search criteria to find the Image you want to add as thumbnail. When the dialog opens, Image as a type is selected by default. However you can narrow the search result by entering additional criteria for searching.
  2. Select the image from the search result
  3. Press the Ok button
